00:12:51,780 --> 00:12:52,700
I can handle it myself.

281
00:13:00,540 --> 00:13:02,660
What nonsense did Liu come up with?

282
00:13:11,420 --> 00:13:13,980
(The Jade Competition has dealt
a heavy blow to the Pei family.)

283
00:13:14,740 --> 00:13:17,820
(If broken jade jewelry
cuts off the Pei family's way out,)

284
00:13:18,620 --> 00:13:20,020
(the Pei family will be at their wits' end.)

285
00:13:20,460 --> 00:13:22,340
(Will they use the Crown then?)

286
00:13:29,180 --> 00:13:30,500
Young Master, why are you here?

287
00:13:30,500 --> 00:13:31,740
I'm angry.

288
00:13:31,740 --> 00:13:33,980
Then don't get angry. It's bad for your health.

289
00:13:33,980 --> 00:13:35,740
Don't you want to ask me why I'm angry?

290
00:13:35,900 --> 00:13:37,260
Why are you angry then?

291
00:13:37,820 --> 00:13:38,660
I...

292
00:13:40,780 --> 00:13:42,100
Since you don't want to say,

293
00:13:42,380 --> 00:13:43,420
I won't ask further.

294
00:13:46,380 --> 00:13:48,540
I'm the young master of Suyu Pavilion.

295
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:50,580
I usually remain calm and composed,

296
00:13:50,820 --> 00:13:52,100
but now I've been pushed

297
00:13:52,100 --> 00:13:54,140
to such heartache by a woman.

298
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:56,940
Young Master, I have never pushed you.

299
00:13:57,060 --> 00:13:57,900
Yes.

300
00:13:57,940 --> 00:13:59,340
It's my own doing, okay?

301
00:13:59,460 --> 00:14:01,180
I saw you embracing Mr. Tan,

302
00:14:01,180 --> 00:14:02,020
being all lovey-dovey.

303
00:14:02,020 --> 00:14:03,700
I'm jealous, resentful, and envious.

304
00:14:04,100 --> 00:14:04,940
Is that okay?

305
00:14:06,860 --> 00:14:08,620
I've been decisive in all my life,

306
00:14:09,020 --> 00:14:10,740
but now I'm so embarrassed like this.

307
00:14:11,180 --> 00:14:12,660
Young Master, you've misunderstood.

308
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:14,700
Mr. Tan is Dandan's old friend.

309
00:14:14,940 --> 00:14:16,980
We just met by chance.

310
00:14:17,340 --> 00:14:18,940
It's not what you think.

311
00:14:19,860 --> 00:14:20,700
You...

312
00:14:21,220 --> 00:14:22,220
You're explaining to me.

313
00:14:22,580 --> 00:14:23,900
You still care about me, right?

314
00:14:24,380 --> 00:14:25,700
I haven't finished talking yet.

315
00:14:26,460 --> 00:14:28,300
Even if I really have something with him,

316
00:14:28,580 --> 00:14:30,300
you're just my master.

317
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:33,140
You don't have to be angry.

318
00:14:43,300 --> 00:14:44,780
Unless their family is on the verge of ruin,

319
00:14:44,780 --> 00:14:46,340
desperate and unable to make ends meet,

320
00:14:47,100 --> 00:14:48,540
then maybe they would

321
00:14:48,940 --> 00:14:51,700
sell off the amber from the Crown.

322
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:56,940
Young Master,

323
00:14:57,060 --> 00:14:59,460
I have something to discuss with you.

324
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:04,300
Qipei Pavilion has been developing
low-cost broken jade jewelry recently.

325
00:15:04,540 --> 00:15:06,580
In fact, I had this idea earlier.

326
00:15:06,940 --> 00:15:08,700
Qipei Pavilion has lost the competition.

327
00:15:08,700 --> 00:15:09,620
Their reputation is damaged.

328
00:15:09,900 --> 00:15:11,740
Their high-priced jade business
has taken a big hit.

329
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:14,100
If we seize the opportunity now

330
00:15:14,100 --> 00:15:16,100
and release low-cost jewelry first,

331
00:15:16,220 --> 00:15:17,780
won't they be at their wits' end?

332
00:15:17,780 --> 00:15:18,940
I don't agree.

333
00:15:22,740 --> 00:15:23,580
Fine.

334
00:15:25,980 --> 00:15:26,820
Fine?

335
00:15:26,820 --> 00:15:27,980
That's it?

336
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:29,980
Will it kill you to beg me once?

337
00:15:30,340 --> 00:15:32,220
Since you think it's unnecessary,

338
00:15:32,380 --> 00:15:34,180
there's no point in discussing it further.

339
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:44,820
Did you really have nothing with Mr. Tan,

340
00:15:44,820 --> 00:15:45,660
like you said?

341
00:15:46,020 --> 00:15:46,860
It's true.

342
00:15:49,420 --> 00:15:50,540
About the jewelry you mentioned earlier,

343
00:15:50,780 --> 00:15:52,180
I'll have people start production tomorrow.

344
00:16:04,780 --> 00:16:06,660
(Delight and Peace)

345
00:16:06,660 --> 00:16:07,500
Wow.

346
00:16:07,580 --> 00:16:09,540
These sample designs
are indeed exquisite and fresh.

347
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:12,260
I didn't expect you, so young,

348
00:16:12,540 --> 00:16:13,460
to have such talent.

349
00:16:13,940 --> 00:16:16,180
Yes. Though these
jewelry pieces aren't expensive,

350
00:16:16,180 --> 00:16:18,220
they will definitely sell out after release.

351
00:16:18,460 --> 00:16:19,340
Oh, stop it.

352
00:16:19,340 --> 00:16:22,060
Thanks to your craftsmanship.

353
00:16:22,220 --> 00:16:23,260
Only when you make them well

354
00:16:23,260 --> 00:16:24,740
can they be sold well.

355
00:16:26,340 --> 00:16:27,180
Young Master,

356
00:16:27,900 --> 00:16:29,500
do we really need to make nice?

357
00:16:29,940 --> 00:16:30,900
This isn't making nice.

358
00:16:31,340 --> 00:16:33,740
This is me being magnanimous and broad-minded.

359
00:16:33,980 --> 00:16:35,020
No need to be on the same level as her.

360
00:16:35,780 --> 00:16:36,620
Besides,

361
00:16:36,740 --> 00:16:37,700
she hasn't mentioned

362
00:16:37,700 --> 00:16:39,780
that fragrant jewelry to me in days.

363
00:16:40,260 --> 00:16:42,220
I can't keep fixating on one thing.

364
00:16:44,980 --> 00:16:46,420
Peach blossom cakes, peach blossom pastries,

365
00:16:46,420 --> 00:16:47,580
and chilled peach blossom hawthorn.

366
00:16:48,060 --> 00:16:49,460
Why all peach blossoms?

367
00:16:49,820 --> 00:16:50,660
Don't you remember?

368
00:16:50,980 --> 00:16:53,380
What did that ugly painter give her back then?

369
00:16:54,660 --> 00:16:55,780
Peach blossom scented powder.

370
00:16:56,100 --> 00:16:56,940
Understood.

371
00:16:56,980 --> 00:16:57,900
Understood, understood.

372
00:16:58,860 --> 00:17:00,380
After eating my peach blossom pastry,

373
00:17:00,780 --> 00:17:02,180
your peach blossom romance will stop.

374
00:17:04,580 --> 00:17:05,460
Ms. Dandan.

375
00:17:06,580 --> 00:17:07,420
Shopkeeper Hao.

376
00:17:08,180 --> 00:17:10,420
70% of the broken jade jewelry
has been completed in production.

377
00:17:10,620 --> 00:17:12,700
We'll start arranging for them
to be shelved in two days.

378
00:17:14,060 --> 00:17:15,220
Regarding these newly arrived styles,

379
00:17:15,220 --> 00:17:16,100
we also need to hurry up.

380
00:17:16,220 --> 00:17:18,620
If the interval is too long,
it might affect sales.

381
00:17:19,460 --> 00:17:21,300
Rest assured. I'm here
keeping a close eye day and night.

382
00:17:21,380 --> 00:17:22,340
We'll be ready to ship out soon.

383
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:23,340
I'll go take a look.

384
00:17:31,540 --> 00:17:32,380
Dandan.

385
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:36,700
This is for you...

386
00:17:36,700 --> 00:17:39,020
Ms. Dandan, Mr. Tan is here looking for you.

387
00:17:39,020 --> 00:17:40,140
He said it was pre-arranged earlier.

388
00:17:43,500 --> 00:17:44,700
I... This...

389
00:17:53,180 --> 00:17:54,020
Let's go.

390
00:17:55,940 --> 00:17:57,700
I often hear Ms. Dandan mentioning you.

391
00:17:57,900 --> 00:18:00,540
Today, it's an honor to meet you.

392
00:18:00,860 --> 00:18:01,940
Madam, your words are too kind.

393
00:18:02,060 --> 00:18:04,900
You are the pillar of the community,
a role model for all of us.

394
00:18:06,780 --> 00:18:07,620
Madam.

395
00:18:13,940 --> 00:18:15,260
- Mother.
- Pei.

396
00:18:19,460 --> 00:18:20,300
Madam.

397
00:18:20,460 --> 00:18:22,660
Mr. Tan has recently opened a perfume shop.

398
00:18:23,220 --> 00:18:24,780
Both its revenue and quality

399
00:18:25,060 --> 00:18:27,060
are among the best in the city.

400
00:18:27,540 --> 00:18:29,100
I invited Mr. Tan over today

401
00:18:29,420 --> 00:18:31,060
mainly to integrate his fragrances

402
00:18:31,340 --> 00:18:33,620
with our jade accessories.

403
00:18:34,340 --> 00:18:35,180
Madam, think about it.

404
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:37,420
If our accessories and jade products

405
00:18:37,660 --> 00:18:38,740
emit fragrances,

406
00:18:39,100 --> 00:18:40,300
wouldn't they be unique

407
00:18:40,540 --> 00:18:41,420
and unparalleled in the world?

408
00:18:46,100 --> 00:18:46,940
Madam,

409
00:18:47,180 --> 00:18:49,940
I wanted to discuss this with the young master.

410
00:18:50,180 --> 00:18:51,060
But the young master

411
00:18:51,700 --> 00:18:53,580
is jealous of Mr. Tan's beauty.

412
00:18:54,820 --> 00:18:57,460
Without any justification, he refused me.

413
00:18:57,460 --> 00:18:58,420
So I had to...

414
00:18:58,420 --> 00:18:59,260
Stay calm, stay calm.

415
00:18:59,340 --> 00:19:00,740
I had to come to you.

416
00:19:01,180 --> 00:19:03,620
Is it feasible to apply fragrance

417
00:19:04,580 --> 00:19:05,420
to jade?

418
00:19:05,620 --> 00:19:07,620
I've been developing many new types
of fragrances recently.

419
00:19:07,980 --> 00:19:10,340
I speculate that whether it's fumigating,
soaking the jade,

420
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:13,220
or applying fragrances

421
00:19:13,420 --> 00:19:14,580
in the form of patches or dots,

422
00:19:14,580 --> 00:19:16,380
- Don't be angry.
- all can be tried.

423
00:19:16,700 --> 00:19:18,500
And as for the lingering time of the fragrance?

424
00:19:18,700 --> 00:19:19,980
As long as the oils are chosen well,

425
00:19:20,540 --> 00:19:21,540
and the attachments are appropriate,

426
00:19:21,940 --> 00:19:24,620
the fragrance should last
for at least six months.

427
00:19:27,180 --> 00:19:28,020
Madam,

428
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:30,540
we can also work with Mr. Tan's perfume shop.

429
00:19:30,940 --> 00:19:32,660
Once this fragrance stops,

430
00:19:32,980 --> 00:19:34,860
we offer lifetime free refills.

431
00:19:35,780 --> 00:19:36,620
Of course,

432
00:19:36,740 --> 00:19:39,500
this cost must be calculated
at the time of initial sale.

433
00:19:39,780 --> 00:19:42,660
In this way, our two families
can cooperate for a long time.

434
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:46,420
I think this is feasible.

435
00:19:46,420 --> 00:19:48,820
Dandan always thinks long-term.

436
00:19:49,260 --> 00:19:50,140
Thank you, Madam.

437
00:19:51,060 --> 00:19:53,180
It's fate for Madam Pei and Dandan

438
00:19:53,340 --> 00:19:55,180
to get to know each other.

439
00:19:55,380 --> 00:19:57,580
It's your mutual blessings.

440
00:19:57,780 --> 00:19:59,620
Yes, that's right.

441
00:20:00,180 --> 00:20:02,460
It's our mutual blessings.

442
00:20:02,740 --> 00:20:04,060
It's my blessing.

443
00:20:04,060 --> 00:20:05,100
I disagree with this matter.

444
00:20:08,940 --> 00:20:10,940
Why are you here causing trouble?

445
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:13,500
Why do you disagree?

446
00:20:14,020 --> 00:20:15,980
It's true we lost in the Jade Competition,

447
00:20:16,420 --> 00:20:17,340
but now

448
00:20:18,020 --> 00:20:19,300
we have broken jade jewelry

449
00:20:19,780 --> 00:20:21,100
and fragrant jewelry,

450
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:24,060
playing some small

451
00:20:24,060 --> 00:20:25,180
and unrefined tricks.

452
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:27,940
When Qipei Pavilion was established,

453
00:20:28,260 --> 00:20:29,820
it was for the refinement of jade carving.

454
00:20:30,500 --> 00:20:31,780
If the ancestors knew

455
00:20:32,100 --> 00:20:33,860
today's Qipei Pavilion is in this situation,

456
00:20:34,340 --> 00:20:35,300
what would they think?

457
00:20:39,580 --> 00:20:40,420
Madam,

458
00:20:40,660 --> 00:20:41,780
no matter what industry it is,

459
00:20:42,020 --> 00:20:43,300
we must let the common people

460
00:20:43,300 --> 00:20:44,820
enjoy the benefits we provide.

461
00:20:45,300 --> 00:20:47,620
If we just hold onto those empty ideals,

462
00:20:48,340 --> 00:20:50,380
aren't we just admiring ourselves in isolation

463
00:20:50,380 --> 00:20:51,340
and deceiving ourselves and others?

464
00:20:54,580 --> 00:20:55,420
I won't let you

465
00:20:55,580 --> 00:20:57,380
and that ugly painter get your way.

466
00:21:00,260 --> 00:21:01,740
You are the ugliest one.

467
00:21:08,460 --> 00:21:09,460
Madam, Young Master.

468
00:21:09,740 --> 00:21:11,340
The City Lord urgently summons
the young master to an audience.

469
00:21:12,140 --> 00:21:12,980
Me?

470
00:21:15,580 --> 00:21:20,260
(Xuanzheng Hall, Yuncui City)

471
00:21:21,540 --> 00:21:25,740
(Xuanzheng Hall)

472
00:21:35,020 --> 00:21:35,860
Greetings, Your Lordship.

473
00:21:36,220 --> 00:21:37,060
No need for formalities.

474
00:21:38,100 --> 00:21:40,060
Look at those jade pieces first.

475
00:21:59,580 --> 00:22:03,220
These jade pieces emit a special fragrance.

476
00:22:03,540 --> 00:22:04,380
Right.

477
00:22:04,540 --> 00:22:06,940
This is the new fragrant jade jewelry
launched by Xiushui City.

478
00:22:07,820 --> 00:22:09,180
Fragrant jade jewelry?

479
00:22:09,340 --> 00:22:11,540
Xiushui City also produces jade,

480
00:22:11,820 --> 00:22:13,860
but the jade material is rough,
and the techniques are ordinary.

481
00:22:14,180 --> 00:22:16,300
It's been trampled underfoot
by the Yuncui City for decades.

482
00:22:16,540 --> 00:22:19,300
Now I don't know where they got the idea.

483
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:21,220
They've produced so much
fragrant jade jewelry,

484
00:22:21,580 --> 00:22:24,100
attracting merchants
from all over the country to buy.

485
00:22:24,420 --> 00:22:25,300
Our Yuncui City,

486
00:22:25,460 --> 00:22:27,300
boasting the reputation of the No. 1 Jade City,

487
00:22:27,900 --> 00:22:30,700
seems to be about to be ignored.

488
00:22:31,340 --> 00:22:33,180
So, you summoned us here

489
00:22:33,340 --> 00:22:35,260
to urge us to expedite the production
of fragrant jade jewelry

490
00:22:35,540 --> 00:22:36,500
to strike at Xiushui City?

491
00:22:36,660 --> 00:22:37,500
That's right.

492
00:22:37,620 --> 00:22:39,340
I order you to produce better goods

493
00:22:39,340 --> 00:22:40,700
in the shortest time possible,

494
00:22:40,860 --> 00:22:42,780
whether it's the quality
of the fragrance or the jade jewelry,

495
00:22:42,940 --> 00:22:44,060
double theirs.

496
00:22:45,620 --> 00:22:47,060
Today, I went to the perfume shop,

497
00:22:47,460 --> 00:22:48,700
and inspiration struck.

498
00:22:49,140 --> 00:22:51,380
I was thinking, women love two things the most.

499
00:22:51,580 --> 00:22:52,500
One is accessories,

500
00:22:52,500 --> 00:22:53,500
and the other is perfume.

501
00:22:53,860 --> 00:22:55,780
If we combine the two,

502
00:22:56,060 --> 00:22:57,420
wouldn't they sell like hotcakes?

503
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:00,580
His Lordship

504
00:23:00,860 --> 00:23:02,860
has planned this for a long time.

505
00:23:03,140 --> 00:23:04,460
Under his efforts and guidance,

506
00:23:04,580 --> 00:23:07,180
Yuncui City's fragrance merchants
are passionate now,

507
00:23:07,380 --> 00:23:09,420
and their quality and standards
have been qualitatively improved.

508
00:23:09,860 --> 00:23:12,380
I believe they will also support your work.

509
00:23:15,140 --> 00:23:15,980
Your Lordship,

510
00:23:16,420 --> 00:23:17,900
I can make fragrant jade jewelry,

511
00:23:18,100 --> 00:23:19,740
and I won't let you down.

512
00:23:20,260 --> 00:23:22,420
But the loser of the Jade Competition,

513
00:23:22,620 --> 00:23:23,980
with their penchant for plagiarism,

514
00:23:24,100 --> 00:23:26,020
doesn't have to work with us.

515
00:23:26,180 --> 00:23:27,020
Alright.

516
00:23:27,100 --> 00:23:29,740
This concerns the reputation
and future of Yuncui City.

517
00:23:29,900 --> 00:23:31,260
Let's not turn on each other.

518
00:23:31,460 --> 00:23:34,340
Qipei Pavilion is still a century-old brand.

519
00:23:34,780 --> 00:23:35,820
With one more person helping,

520
00:23:35,940 --> 00:23:37,380
I can be a bit more at ease.

521
00:23:39,140 --> 00:23:39,980
Yes.

522
00:23:40,220 --> 00:23:41,060
Pei Pei.

523
00:23:41,580 --> 00:23:42,420
During this period,

524
00:23:42,660 --> 00:23:44,300
you should communicate closely with Su Jue,

525
00:23:44,460 --> 00:23:45,340
cooperate sincerely,

526
00:23:45,460 --> 00:23:47,220
achieve results, and make contributions.

527
00:23:47,620 --> 00:23:48,820
As for the plagiarism incident before,

528
00:23:49,100 --> 00:23:50,700
His Lordship won't pursue it further.

529
00:23:52,020 --> 00:23:54,260
Fragrant jade jewelry is of utmost importance.

530
00:23:54,700 --> 00:23:56,660
The Pei family will spare no effort.

531
00:23:56,980 --> 00:23:59,020
However, regarding this plagiarism matter,

532
00:23:59,620 --> 00:24:01,820
I believe the innocent
will prove their innocence.

533
00:24:02,300 --> 00:24:04,220
Alright. Hurry and get to work.

534
00:24:27,340 --> 00:24:28,620
What are you laughing at?

535
00:24:28,980 --> 00:24:29,940
Laughing at your foolishness.

536
00:24:30,300 --> 00:24:31,860
Officially appointed by the City Lord's decree,

537
00:24:31,860 --> 00:24:33,180
you have to do it now.

538
00:24:33,580 --> 00:24:34,820
If only you had listened to me earlier,

539
00:24:35,020 --> 00:24:36,860
we would've saved all this trouble now, right?

540
00:24:37,540 --> 00:24:38,380
Yes.

541
00:24:38,700 --> 00:24:40,900
It seems you truly are favored by heaven.

542
00:24:41,580 --> 00:24:42,420
With you around,

543
00:24:42,620 --> 00:24:44,300
everything goes smoothly.

544
00:24:47,060 --> 00:24:47,940
Aren't you afraid

545
00:24:47,940 --> 00:24:51,620
I'll get too close to that ugly painter?

546
00:24:53,220 --> 00:24:55,980
Now my horizons have broadened.

547
00:25:15,540 --> 00:25:16,900
Mr. Tan and I

548
00:25:17,260 --> 00:25:20,220
are just regular friends.

549
00:25:22,740 --> 00:25:23,700
Since the City Lord has tasked us

550
00:25:23,700 --> 00:25:25,260
with developing fragrant jade jewelry,

551
00:25:25,660 --> 00:25:26,980
we should set aside our suspicions

552
00:25:26,980 --> 00:25:27,820
and double our efforts.

