571
00:26:28,660 --> 00:26:29,500
Exactly.

572
00:26:29,540 --> 00:26:31,500
So, Qipei Pavilion's renewed glory

573
00:26:31,660 --> 00:26:32,980
depends on the two of us.

574
00:26:34,020 --> 00:26:35,180
