706
00:34:07,580 --> 00:34:08,420
What are you doing?

707
00:34:08,740 --> 00:34:09,580
Hurry up and praise me.

708
00:34:10,060 --> 00:34:10,900
Of course.

709
00:34:11,180 --> 00:34:14,100
You really are an ordinary little genius.

710
00:34:14,940 --> 00:34:17,500
But the color of this limestone is too dull.

711
00:34:18,060 --> 00:34:19,060
If we could switch

712
00:34:19,060 --> 00:34:20,900
to Dongling stone,
which blends better with jade,

713
00:34:20,900 --> 00:34:22,020
